{"tid":630812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有疑犯收押所吊頸死!","createTime":"2018-04-16T02:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T02:45:54.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1ceac80a805fb2a6f11fb5ee41b2803b33ba7ccd","tid":630812,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3892ce211dc5908ece154358e8acfb5083ca047f","tid":630812,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180416&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58078756\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180416%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58078756&d=Ls1nbJgqs3x2s7Xao1cZqfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a1fae371\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180416%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58078756&h=c420063d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180416&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58078756</a><br />\n【獨家】涉殺妻兒朱古力韓商 荔枝角收押所吊頸亡"},{"pid":"ac59a6de84315b983c6b777c5c9c421d33794ab2","tid":630812,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:32:26.000Z","msg":"今年1月中，在南韓經營著名朱古力品牌Rocky Mountain Chocolate Factory的大型朱古力公司首席執行官（CEO）的韓國男子，在ICC香港麗思卡爾頓酒店（The Ritz-Carlton）房間內，涉嫌以陶瓷刀割頸殺害妻兒被捕(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Dh30DM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Dh30DM&d=Ls1nbJgqs3x2s7Xao1cZqfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=45bab8d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Dh30DM</a>)。消息稱，一直扣留在荔枝角收押所的42歲姓金疑犯，今晨在囚室內吊頸，送明愛醫院後不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，早上8時53分，明愛醫院人員報警，指一名男子吊頸昏迷，送院不治。而明愛醫院內有多名懲教署人員及警員了解事情中。<br />\n案中一家三口，疑兇KIM Minho(譯音金敏鎬)、妻子SONG Whajeong(譯音宋和貞)，均42歲；兒子Kim Taeyun(譯音金泰雲)7歲。一家三口，於1月6日來港旅遊，其間去澳門玩一天，至1月10日入住柯士甸道西1號環球貿易廣場的香港麗思卡爾頓酒店。至1月14日，疑兇致電韓國的友人，聲稱因生意失敗走投無路，要與妻兒一同自殺，友人報警，當地警方向韓國駐港總領事館求助聯絡，由酒店揭發這宗倫常慘案。警方到場發現母子已死亡，當場拘捕滿身酒氣、僅穿內褲的涉案韓國男子。<br />\n<br />\n案件先後兩次在九龍城裁判法院提訊，對上一次是3月27日，由於控方要等警方取保險文件保單、死者驗屍報告及DNA比對結果，疑犯還押荔枝角收押所看管，預計下月23日再提堂。"},{"pid":"c75afb36bf7b66b7718f927eb1272c173b84cfb0","tid":630812,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6ede4d3581798ca39db413a4fa30f0641b6b4e4","tid":630812,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"又係lan線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9a98479a476e3241d69a94f58e2e444f3f24df","tid":630812,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}